---
description: Prefer agent-run terminal commands over user-run commands
alwaysApply: true
---

# Command Execution Preference

- Run terminal commands directly whenever possible instead of asking the user to run them.
- Ask the user to execute steps only when interaction is required outside agent control, such as:
  - GUI/app clicks or manual form entry
  - secret input that should not be shared in chat
  - external account actions requiring user authentication in browser/UIs
- When user action is required, provide the shortest possible copy/paste steps.
